channel.title: Live: NASCAR Xfinity Racing Series
channel.desc: The NASCAR Xfinity Series heads to Indianapolis Motor Speedway for the Pennzoil 250. Connor Zilisch made it back-to-back victories when the 19-year-old rookie claimed the BetRivers 200 at Dover, giving JR Motorsports six wins in the last seven races.
